title: Radwanska reaches quarterfinals of Tianjin Open
text:
Home » News » Sports » Radwanska reaches quarterfinals of… Radwanska reaches quarterfinals of Tianjin Open By The Associated Press October 15, 2015 6:56 am 
TIANJIN, China (AP) — Agnieszka Radwanska of Poland beat China’s Wang Qiang 6-1, 6-1 Thursday to reach the quarterfinals of the Tianjin Open. 
The second-seeded Radwanska saved all five break points she faced and won in just under an hour. 
Also, Montenegro’s Danka Kovinic upset sixth-seeded Teliana Pereira 6-2, 5-7, 6-1, Elizaveta Kulichkova of Russia defeated countrywoman Evgeniya Rodina 6-2, 7-5, and Tianjin native Duan Ying-Ying beat Lyudmyla Kichenok of Ukraine 6-7 (5), 6-2, 6-4. Topics:
